Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:07.59,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,An employee directory dating back to ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:10.57,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,It should be sufficient if we're able to trace the records to that extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:17.24,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,If we can find the corporate spies who stole them, the identity of the contractor who's after them will eventually turn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:20.21,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Still don't know where Mao is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:23.04,DTB-Default,Ying,0,0,0,,I'm searching for him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.03,0:00:29.21,DTB-Default,Yabuta,0,0,0,,We're from the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.68,0:00:32.84,DTB-Default,Yabuta,0,0,0,,There are a few things we'd like to ask you, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:36.42,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,W-Where the hell am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:46.73,DTB-Default,Yabuta,0,0,0,,Dental records identified the corpse as Katsuragi Toshiko, the owner of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:52.74,DTB-Default,Yabuta,0,0,0,,It's only natural to conclude that she fell as she leaned on the banister, which gave under her weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:56.48,DTB-Default,Yabuta,0,0,0,,It seemed plausible, since it was an old house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:01:00.34,DTB-Default,Yabuta,0,0,0,,That's why it would have been filed as a mere accident
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:04.35,DTB-Default,Yabuta,0,0,0,,until you came into the picture, Matsukichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.55,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I threw away that name along with my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:13.31,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,My name is Gai, Kurasawa Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:16.14,DTB-Default,Yabuta,0,0,0,,What are you showing off for, you idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:22.19,DTB-Default,Yabuta,0,0,0,,Is there any connection between the cosmetic company suicides and this incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:28.46,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I left that job because I was sick of the lack of imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:33.12,DTB-Default,Yabuta,0,0,0,,The reason you quit being a cop was because you never had any sense of imagination, period.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.12,0:01:35.67,DTB-Default,Yabuta,0,0,0,,Detective work doesn't suit you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.23,0:01:38.89,DTB-Default,Yabuta,0,0,0,,You should go back to your homeland
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:43.34,DTB-Default,Yabuta,0,0,0,,for your own sake, Matsukichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:48.16,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,My name is Kurasawa Gai, private investigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:50.21,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,It definitely isn't Matsukichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:56.62,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,The case that started out as a search for a cat has developed into one about an ex-wife's mysterious death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:02:05.53,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,My intuition tells me it'll develop into an even bigger case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:10.97,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,I found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:23.75,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You're not going to your part-time job at this time of night, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:25.93,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Why are you loitering around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.93,0:02:27.88,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong with taking a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.72,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Around here, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:32.56,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,The stars are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:35.05,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:38.17,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? It's overcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.43,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:51.23,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I suppose they questioned you about every single detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:55.20,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,The police are rather insensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:57.02,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I apologize on their behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:03:01.01,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,No, it's not something you should be apologizing for, Mr. Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:04.18,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,About the cat that was found...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:05.42,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:06.66,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Yes, the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:09.79,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Oh, that cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:11.42,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It wasn't her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:14.93,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It was a different black cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:20.18,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,It resembled her quite a bit, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:22.18,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It's completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:26.77,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,My Mii-chan has a more sophisticated face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:29.19,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Damn! If I could only use the wireless...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:39.39,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,This is bad. Am I going to be sent to the pound?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:59.71,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,While Toshiko was still married to Yuzuki, she came to my place one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:02.60,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,His former wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:07.61,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Yes. She told me to break off the relationship with Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:12.26,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,She spoke in an elegant manner, without the slightest change in her voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:16.30,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,but her eyes were terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:19.80,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,That must have been a frightening moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:26.22,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It was then when I noticed she wasn't wearing any perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:29.80,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:35.22,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,My husband didn't tell that woman to wear perfume,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:38.59,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,which meant that he didn't dislike her body odor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:43.89,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,I became mortified for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:46.39,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you feel the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.56,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,A person's body odor is an intrinsic trait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:53.84,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It was as if he told me I looked better with heavy makeup instead of none at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:07.24,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,There was more to her relationship with Toshiko than I had thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:11.26,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,By simple deduction, she was the one responsible for Toshiko's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:13.71,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,No, it can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:22.09,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,C-Cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.57,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,H-H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:27.26,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Are you telling me to take this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:37.09,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,That reminds me. That glutton was hanging around Toshiko's house, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.09,0:05:39.67,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he was the one who did that to Toshiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:41.18,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:44.69,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Damn. Everyone's suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:48.74,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Hey, don't interrupt me while I'm thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:53.39,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,What the hell am I supposed to do with this cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:57.55,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I might as well throw him into the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:06:01.31,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Hey! Animal cruelty of that magnitude isn't tolerated these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:02.49,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:09.81,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,I'm not going to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:14.32,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,Return that jacket without saying a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:18.32,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You're the one I met at the open air cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:19.57,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,He's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:22.08,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Are you after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:23.37,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:24.52,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,Hand over the jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:28.84,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I get it. Are you involved in this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:30.70,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You are, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:32.84,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,Case?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:36.10,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,It looks like you do know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:37.98,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,What do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:40.76,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,Are you a contractor as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.61,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:45.07,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,A contract to kill the former wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:47.26,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,Former wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:48.52,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:49.94,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:53.02,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,If you have no intention of returning it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.84,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,This is the worst host ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:10.46,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,He has athlete's foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.96,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,He possessed that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:23.55,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,You should have returned the jacket without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:26.72,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:30.02,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,It's inside this jacket, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:33.31,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Au revoir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:39.42,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Getting used to an unfamiliar host is so annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:48.92,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,This crow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:50.95,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.97,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,You're the cat from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:58.36,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,So you're a possession-type contractor, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:00.53,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,What if I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:03.17,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,You've lost it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.11,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.21,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,Your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.31,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:18.19,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:21.02,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,Another contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.78,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Move to his blind side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.78,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,He won't be able to possess your body if you stay away from his line of sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:53.06,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:59.02,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Hei! Shit! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:10.53,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode Eight The Scent of Gardenias Lingers in the Summer Rain... (Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:19.50,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:21.83,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,What were you doing swimming at this time of year?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:25.12,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.73,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,You shouldn't stick your nose into frivolous matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.14,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,You're going to lose your balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:32.82,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,A man's job is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:36.07,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Did you find the cat, Miss Flat Chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:39.06,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Again with the sexual harassment...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:41.62,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Oh, about that garbage mansion case...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:44.28,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,It looked interesting, so I checked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:47.79,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,If you get too involved in this case, you'll have your balls taken as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.57,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Not that you have any to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:52.33,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,I'll seriously sue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:56.97,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,More importantly, I heard a strange rumor around the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:59.32,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,It's about this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.10,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,The widow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:02.50,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:19.57,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Now that's bureaucracy at its finest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:22.22,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,They've finally taken action.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:25.80,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.20,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Is this from Huang?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:35.26,DTB-Default,Ying,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.96,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Doesn't seem like there's any doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:39.79,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What do you think, Mao?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:42.47,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.63,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:47.33,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,I was just receiving data from the network.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.43,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Network?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:50.83,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Haven't I told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:55.02,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,The deficient brain capacity of a cat is compensated by a server.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:11:01.27,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,If I don't do this occasionally, the feline conscience becomes dominant, just like when I was lost in that garbage mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:03.33,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,That's him all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:06.78,DTB-Default,Ying,0,0,0,,Ukiyama Norio, a manipulator of gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:08.20,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Gravity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:09.98,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Doesn't he use possession?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:11.48,DTB-Default,Ying,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:14.08,DTB-Default,Ying,0,0,0,,Together with another contractor that has the ability to possess bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:18.44,DTB-Default,Ying,0,0,0,,who goes by the name of Amitabh Kapoor, they've been particularly active in North India.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.84,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:21.53,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:24.76,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Kapoor possessed Ukiyama's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:30.96,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,However, due to an accident during the possession, Kapoor lost his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.87,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Where have I heard that story before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:41.20,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,According to the police, the ex-wife had a chronic heart condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:43.40,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:47.78,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,She probably suffered a heart attack while she was walking along the staircase,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:50.62,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,when she leaned on the banister and unfortunately fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:54.32,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,There's little doubt about whether it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:56.11,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:56.75,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,However?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:02.56,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:05.78,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:07.30,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:11.80,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Why did you have me go to the ex-wife's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:13.43,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It was because of my cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:16.63,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,There's no way she could have taken the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:19.56,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Remember the trend some time ago
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:23.57,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,when people used to place plastic bottles filled with water to ward off cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:30.19,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,It would be difficult to imagine someone who disliked cats that much would take her, even if it was to annoy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:35.17,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You were looking for someone to send to that house from the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:41.24,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,in order to find her body and frame as the killer, in the best case scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:48.74,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I have a witness who saw you near Toshiko-san's house almost six months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:52.30,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,the estimated time of her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:55.36,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You had plenty of motives to have her dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:13:00.02,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You're the perpetrator, aren't you, madam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:02.52,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:04.14,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I don't have any evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:06.04,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Call it an investigator's intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:08.92,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Madam, I didn't want to acknowledge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:11.76,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Turn yourself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:16.62,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:21.07,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It isn't possible for evidence to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:24.05,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,She was already dead by the time I went to visit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:28.47,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,I certainly went there six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:34.40,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,I had overheard her house had become a garbage mansion, so I wanted to see for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:36.11,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Why would you do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:40.48,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It was Yuzuki's home since he was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:44.48,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,I couldn't stand the thought of it being tainted by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:48.73,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It was worse than I imagined it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:52.49,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,I couldn't restrain myself, so I went in to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.70,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Is she away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:09.34,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,However, believe me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:13.80,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,I didn't ask you to go to the mansion to frame you as the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:19.56,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Having her body not be found for such a long time and left neglected like that slightly scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:24.30,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,In any case, I was being used.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:26.10,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:30.14,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Why didn't you notify the authorities at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:33.38,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,I didn't want to be involved in the investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:35.83,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:38.70,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,That's how I felt about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:51.34,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Are you the one who called me out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.76,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,but it had crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:15:00.75,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,The body odor of the woman Yuzuki liked should turn into a rotten musk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:16.72,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,She deserved to rot amongst garbage and emit a vile stench.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.33,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Why did you go that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:25.33,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,It seems to me you were the one who stole him from his ex-wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:31.09,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,The reason why she trashed her own house could have been triggered by the shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:34.67,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You're the one who gained everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:36.97,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,What did I really gain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:44.91,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Yuzuki covetously used all of his senses...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:47.98,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Looking, feeling, licking...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:54.20,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,If it was limited to that, I couldn't lose against Toshiko's aging body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:56.09,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:58.39,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,from Yuzuki's perspective,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:00.20,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,everything was about smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:01.88,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:05.17,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Yes, he had an obsession for odor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:10.69,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,That person truly smelled every single detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:16.13,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It was as if every part of my body had been exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:20.68,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,But the odor he really loved
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.45,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,wasn't my scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:28.27,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,Once I receive the goods from you, I'm saying farewell to this miserable country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:31.66,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,How unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:34.36,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.55,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.57,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It's a strange feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:07.47,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,When you experience that kind of treatment, you begin to believe that body odor has real significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.67,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,How can I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:12.86,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It's as if it becomes a part of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:18.37,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,In hindsight, the only thing I obtained was the title of a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:23.60,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,I could never get what I really wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:26.41,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:30.85,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,It's what the corporate spies took and what he tried to steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:33.48,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,It's probably related to the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.05,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:41.94,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Let's go, Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:44.54,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Mao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:48.06,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,He was sniffing a sock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:50.48,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,His remuneration, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:53.22,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,He didn't have any time to use his abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.29,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:58.38,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,He probably just wanted to smell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:02.57,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,There's no way to understand how a contractor thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.66,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.83,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,He just wanted to smell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:12.10,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,If this sock was originally his,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:18.36,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,the scent of this sock would be the only remaining evidence of his physical past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:22.30,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,He probably completed his remuneration
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.30,0:18:26.36,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,when he lost his body, like I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:31.31,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,It's raining again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:33.43,DTB-Default,Maid,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.69,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Is there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:42.45,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:56.06,DTB-Default,Rika,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:57.16,DTB-Default,Rika,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:01.09,DTB-Default,Rika,0,0,0,,Oh, Hernandez?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:03.59,DTB-Default,Rika,0,0,0,,Or is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:08.61,DTB-Default,Rika,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:12.69,DTB-Default,Rika,0,0,0,,You lost something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:17.82,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,In the end, the cat was never found.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:24.82,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,It might have been a farce from the beginning. A lost cat may have never existed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:26.82,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:30.64,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I received the remaining payments in the name of grievance money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.29,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,The case was closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.37,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,I found that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:42.46,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,He was at the Home Run Ken eating enough ramen to die from!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:43.85,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,He's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:46.32,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Can I stalk him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:48.26,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:53.02,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Since then, I occasionally see that young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:56.35,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Upon further investigation, I've come to the conclusion that he's just a glutton.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:59.23,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,What was I suspecting him of?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:02.78,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,So goes the saying, "suspicion begets fear".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.96,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Mao, Huang is looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:10.75,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,What? I was in the middle of a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:13.54,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Do you have dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:15.26,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:18.16,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,They're all trivial dreams, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:23.26,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,About eating, bathing, frivolous stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:31.26,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Sleeping all day without being yelled at is probably the only good thing about being a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:34.82,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,What's with the gloomy face?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:39.25,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,You're supposed to laugh at that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:44.28,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The reunion of a friend is an ominous twist of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:48.51,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The memories of her school days are faint,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:50.82,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,leaving only the lingering scent of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:54.41,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The scheme underneath the white dress conceals
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:58.42,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,a dark conspiracy and a bloodbath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:01.28,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The stone-like glitter of the flower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:04.93,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,is cold and drives people insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:08.39,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The party has just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:09.29,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an2\c&HE3E3E3&\pos(640,552)}Episode Nine The White Dress, Stained with the Girl's Dreams and Blood... (Part One)